com.ichess.game

Class PGN

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ichess.game.PGN

  • public class PGN
extends java.lang.Object
    PGN allow recording a game and information about the game. A Game can be loaded from a PGN string and vice versa.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ran Berenfeld
    See Also:
    PGN specification
